<paragraph id="DE193690B72528570C90FC943881FC24" pageId="0" pageNumber="348">• Small to medium-sized monkeys with hindlimbs longer than forelimbs, head oval in squirrel monkeys and rounded in capuchins, relatively large brain, large ears, and long tail that is semi-prehensile in capuchins.</paragraph>
